                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5031109_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5031109_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7375756">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7375756/" class="title-link">这本书不厚道啊，只是2010年的翻版，买了才发现...</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7375756"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1416401/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1416401-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1416401/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">minblue</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-02-11"
      class="main-meta">2015-02-11 13:16:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7375756_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  还以为是新的内容，买了才知道是个骗钱的玩意，买过10年精装版的《生命八卦》的可以无视这本书了。 10年精装版的《生命八卦》地址如下http://book.douban.com/subject/4268931/

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7375756/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 1没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            生活·读书·新知三联书店2015版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7375756_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7375756_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
